<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" dir="ltr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tirsam Groupe | Poids lourds & Bus</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background: #f4f4f4;
            color: #1e1e2a;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1300px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .navbar {
            background: #0a2b3e;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .navbar .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .logo span {
            color: #f39c12;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 25px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #f39c12;
        }
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2c39, #1b4f6e);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 70px 20px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #f39c12;
            color: #1e1e2a;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #e67e22;
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }
        .category-title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin: 40px 0 20px;
            border-right: 5px solid #f39c12;
            padding-right: 15px;
        }
        .product-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }
        .card-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #eef2f5;
        }
        .card-img img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .card:hover .card-img img {
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }
        .card-content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .card-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .specs {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .price {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e67e22;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .btn-small {
            background: #0a2b3e;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-small:hover {
            background: #f39c12;
            color: #1e1e2a;
        }
        footer {
            background: #0a2b3e;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">Tirsam <span>Groupe</span></div>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="#camions">Camions SITRAK</a>
                <a href="#bus51">Bus 51 places</a>
                <a href="#bus100">Bus 100 places</a>
                <a href="formulaire.html" class="btn-small" style="background:#f39c12; color:#1e1e2a;">Demande info</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Fabrication & assemblage de véhicules industriels</h1>
            <p>Camions SITRAK • Bus 51 & 100 places • Fiabilité allemande (MAN)</p>
            <a href="formulaire.html" class="btn">Obtenir un devis</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div id="camions">
            <div class="category-title">🚛 Camions SITRAK (Moteurs MAN)</div>
            <div class="product-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-img">
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/0a2b3e/white?text=SITRAK+4x2" alt="SITRAK 4x2">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>SITRAK 4×2</h3>
                        <div class="specs">• Porteur / Tracteur<br>• Moteur 320 ch • Boîte ZF</div>
                        <div class="price">À partir de 9 800 000 DA</div>
                        <a href="formulaire.html?modele=SITRAK%204x2" class="btn-small">Demander un prix</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-img">
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/1b4f6e/white?text=SITRAK+6x4" alt="SITRAK 6x4">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>SITRAK 6×4</h3>
                        <div class="specs">• 3 essieux • 400 ch<br>• Idéal pour chantiers et mines</div>
                        <div class="price">À partir de 12 500 000 DA</div>
                        <a href="formulaire.html?modele=SITRAK%206x4" class="btn-small">Demander un prix</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-img">
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/2c3e50/white?text=SITRAK+8x4" alt="SITRAK 8x4">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>SITRAK 8×4</h3>
                        <div class="specs">• 4 essieux • Benne / Bétonnière<br>• Puissance 460 ch</div>
                        <div class="price">À partir de 16 200 000 DA</div>
                        <a href="formulaire.html?modele=SITRAK%208x4" class="btn-small">Demander un prix</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="bus51">
            <div class="category-title">🚌 Bus 51 places (TS11)</div>
            <div class="product-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-img">
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/2ecc71/white?text=Bus+51+places" alt="Bus 51 places">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Bus 51 voyageurs</h3>
                        <div class="specs">• Climatisation • Confort Européen<br>• Distribution ETUSA, Sétram, etc.</div>
                        <div class="price">13 500 000 DA</div>
                        <a href="formulaire.html?modele=Bus%2051%20places%20(13.5M)" class="btn-small">Demander un prix</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="bus100">
            <div class="category-title">🚍 Bus 100 places (Haut standing)</div>
            <div class="product-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-img">
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/3498db/white?text=Bus+100+places" alt="Bus 100 places">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Bus 100 voyageurs</h3>
                        <div class="specs">• Électrique ou Diesel • Normes Euro 6<br>• Livraison possible sous 6 mois</div>
                        <div class="price">Sur devis (à partir de 22 000 000 DA)</div>
                        <a href="formulaire.html?modele=Bus%20100%20places" class="btn-small">Demander un prix</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2026 Tirsam Groupe - Tous droits réservés | Siège : Batna, Zone industrielle Kechida | <a href="formulaire.html" style="color:#f39c12;">Contact commercial</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
